FBIS3-41540 "jpten004___94010" JPRS-TEN-94-004 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Environmental Issues 17 February 1994 CHINA Asian Development Bank Assists Environmental Project OW2311174493 Beijing XINHUA in English 1703 GMT 23 Nov 93 OW2311174493 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Manila, Nov 23 (XINHUA) -- The Asian Development Bank has approved a technical assistance grant of 900,000 U.S. dollars to China for the second phase of an environmental impact assessment (EIA) training project. The aim of the project is to train some 20,000 specialists from government departments, companies and institutions in how to use the EIA process as a key environmental planning tool. The assistance is financed from the Japan Special Fund.
